svg.title: Trained at Accomplis + Before becoming a co + Nesreen Mahmoud, Fou

g.text: Trained at Accomplishment Coaching and The Grief
Recovery Institute®, Nesreen offers a unique blend of life
and bereavement coaching that helps her clients move
through difficult experiences and remove the obstacles to
becoming their most authentic, empowered selves. She has
also studied psychology and childhood development at The
New School University, speech pathology at The University
of Southern Florida and Utah State University, and
international relations at The College of William and Mary.
She founded Harbor Light Coaching in 2015.
Before becoming a coach, Nesreen spent 15 years working as a costumer for the Broadway stage, television,
and film. She’s worked on shows including Beautiful: The Carole King Musical, Monty Python’s Spamalot,
The Producers, The Radio City Christmas Spectacular, Madame Secretary, and The Affair.
